{"tid":2277160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁弓夷可能已經比Trump更加接近 Deep State 權力核心","createTime":"2020-11-08T09:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T17:10:35.000Z","uid":118346,"like":56,"dislike":133,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"bd171239b4f92504528ac21bc8a2be821c1c8f8c","tid":2277160,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s0eOIBWgeuc?t=3611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs0eOIBWgeuc%3Ft%3D3611&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq72Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=8dbc7541\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s0eOIBWgeuc?t=3611</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n袁爸提到佢比美國一個維珍尼亞既老煙草家族請去食飯講天賦人權，嚇到我彈起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先維珍尼亞州既有錢家族唔係一般既有錢人<br />\n維珍尼亞係英國第一個美國殖民地，係美國革命第一個州，亦都好近華盛頓<br />\n所以佢地一直係有錢、有理想、有家教、亦都有好大既政治影響力，一路都keep住美國立國既精神<br />\n<br />\n呢D家族有個名：First Families of Virginia<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/First_Families_of_Virginia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFirst_Families_of_Virginia&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq72Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=6a7c6b28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/First_Families_of_Virginia</a><br />\n<br />\n最重要既係維珍尼亞呢D家族係1912年成立過一個世襲組織：<strong>Order of the First Families of Virginia</strong>，呢個唔係秘密組織。但係知道歐美上層文化既人（我信肯定有連登仔知得多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）都知係呢D Order入面先可以同最重要既人傾計<br />\n<br />\nSolomon Yue收料係好準，但係佢係西岸，而且都算係政治人物<br />\n反而袁弓夷作為商人，而家先係地理上同人脈上更加接近美國當前權力核心<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>其實袁爸群埋邊個都唔重要<br />\n重要係大家要聽清楚佢最近意識到既野：</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\">香港人<ins><strong>暗啞底既諗法可能已經同美國立國元勛高度相似</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">藍絲口中既<br />\n「打拼就有錢」、「有錢就有權」</span><br />\n對比<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>Pompeo既Inalienable Rights<br />\n「不可剝奪的天賦人權」<br />\n<br />\n同我地既諗法其實相差無幾</strong></span><br />\n</span></p>"},{"pid":"ebdf244e0b295bd001aefe772d423f60fd5fab28","tid":2277160,"uid":48631,"like":135,"dislike":14,"score":121,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"大紀袁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be34498e7161e5f333515144bc32ff68178872cc","tid":2277160,"uid":125831,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"準？<br />\n屌佢已經燈左好撚多獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b27c4b8c2c32b762b43b0229e4c25929db442f","tid":2277160,"uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"呢個OP而家彈起落返地未"},{"pid":"a55392edee19f410dc948826ad97389c06120ef6","tid":2277160,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d9b11af6c542a45e30e703c238f451335d81a9","tid":2277160,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebdf244e0b295bd001aefe772d423f60fd5fab28","tid":2277160,"uid":48631,"like":135,"dislike":14,"score":121,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"大紀袁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7ad52fc3dce06385d38a3ee73fd53f7b2dc525","tid":2277160,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"估唔到deep state 入邊都分咗咁多派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2