ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）都知係呢D Order入面先可以同最重要既人傾計<br />\n<br />\nSolomon Yue收料係好準，但係佢係西岸，而且都算係政治人物<br />\n反而袁弓夷作為商人，而家先係地理上同人脈上更加接近美國當前權力核心<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>其實袁爸群埋邊個都唔重要<br />\n重要係大家要聽清楚佢最近意識到既野：</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\">香港人<ins><strong>暗啞底既諗法可能已經同美國立國元勛高度相似</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">藍絲口中既<br />\n「打拼就有錢」、「有錢就有權」</span><br />\n對比<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>Pompeo既Inalienable Rights<br />\n「不可剝奪的天賦人權」<br />\n<br />\n同我地既諗法其實相差無幾</strong></span><br />\n</span></p>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T10:10:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c2CwPCbkgXk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc2CwPCbkgXk&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq72Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=69842e4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c2CwPCbkgXk</a><br />\n<br />\n侵爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 偽民主必亡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6c826190d2507f891d76129a3797c73d0f0dc4","tid":2277160,"uid":78440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ebdf244e0b295bd001aefe772d423f60fd5fab28","tid":2277160,"uid":48631,"like":135,"dislike":14,"score":121,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"大紀袁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"創意無限，極為精辟，言簡意賅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmo